q(uk+1) = q(uk) + q (uk)δu + O((δu)2) ≈ q(uk) + q (uk)δu,

(1.80)

and dropping other nonlinear terms in δu, we get

∇ · q(uk)∇uk + ∇ · q(uk)∇δu + ∇ · q (uk)δu∇uk = 0.

